 <PERSON> John </PERSON> <PERSON> King </PERSON> of the The <ORGANIZATION> Associated </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Press </ORGANIZATION> covered <PERSON> Michael </PERSON> <PERSON> Dukakis </PERSON> as governor in <LOCATION> Boston </LOCATION> and is now reporting on the national presidential campaign.
