 and 1986 crop corn and sorghum extended loans which mature on March 31 through Dec. 31 this _ 1984 crop FOR loans which mature on March 31 through Dec. 31 this year In addition, he said, 1987 crops of wheat and feed grains will not be permitted to enter the FOR.
